1
00:01:07,601 --> 00:01:10,941
Daemons of the Shadow Realm

2
00:01:11,741 --> 00:01:14,851
All the pain I've experienced

3
00:01:18,361 --> 00:01:23,221
Has traveled through my veins

4
00:01:25,161 --> 00:01:28,361
And passed through my heart

5
00:01:32,041 --> 00:01:35,461
By the time I've forgotten, it arrives

6
00:01:35,461 --> 00:01:36,571
In my brain

7
00:01:36,571 --> 00:01:38,611
I guess it's not that bad

8
00:01:38,611 --> 00:01:41,641
But there's this tiny little draft

9
00:01:41,641 --> 00:01:46,141
Of resentment and sadness

10
00:01:46,141 --> 00:01:49,991
Just let me have this

11
00:01:50,441 --> 00:01:53,571
I'm spineless

12
00:01:53,571 --> 00:01:57,161
All my words and tears

13
00:01:57,161 --> 00:02:00,861
And these feathers grown from my feelings

14
00:02:00,861 --> 00:02:03,951
I'll put all of them on my back

15
00:02:03,951 --> 00:02:07,101
Well, see you later

16
00:02:07,101 --> 00:02:10,921
I'll leave it all behind here

17
00:02:10,921 --> 00:02:12,191
I'm not scared

18
00:02:12,191 --> 00:02:14,211
Up in the sky

19
00:02:14,211 --> 00:02:17,331
See these feathers flutter in the wind

20
00:02:17,331 --> 00:02:23,171
And follow along

21
00:04:48,781 --> 00:04:51,291
Episode 2
 Left and Right

22
00:12:39,541 --> 00:12:41,051
Daemons of the Shadow Realm

23
00:12:42,661 --> 00:12:45,541
Old Higashi Village Trailhead

24
00:15:28,251 --> 00:15:31,501
Old Higashi Village Trailhead

25
00:15:38,001 --> 00:15:39,671
We're at the sign 2 km from the
Old Higashi Village Trailhead

26
00:15:38,001 --> 00:15:39,501
Waiting

27
00:15:38,001 --> 00:15:41,881
Where are you now?

28
00:15:39,211 --> 00:15:42,511
On my way!

29
00:15:39,381 --> 00:15:42,511
I should be there soon

30
00:22:06,651 --> 00:22:09,611
Keep watching me

31
00:22:09,611 --> 00:22:14,441
So I can't leave

32
00:22:19,251 --> 00:22:21,861
Hold me

33
00:22:22,421 --> 00:22:27,311
So I won't start crying

34
00:22:30,591 --> 00:22:33,671
A tailwind blows

35
00:22:33,671 --> 00:22:43,101
A thread runs down my spine, and when it reaches my bloodstream

36
00:22:44,821 --> 00:22:46,281
Ah

37
00:22:46,281 --> 00:22:56,401
I've found wings that might let me fly again

38
00:22:56,941 --> 00:22:59,021
Maybe

39
00:22:59,021 --> 00:23:06,371
If you haven't left the nest yet

40
00:23:06,371 --> 00:23:12,931
Then we can fly together

41
00:23:26,651 --> 00:23:28,031
Next Episode
 Preview

42
00:23:37,041 --> 00:23:40,041
Episode 3
 Dera and Hana
